solution: ```class Solution {
public:
    string defangIPaddr(string address) {
        string res;
        res.reserve(address.size() + 6);
        for (char c : address) {
            if (c == '.') res += "[.]";
            else res += c;
        }
        return res;
    }
};
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(n)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Single pass through the string, pre-allocating the result buffer to avoid reallocations. Direct character checks and appends yield minimal CPU and memory usage.

